ed="T" n="0731c13"/><persName key="A002451">釋德感</persName>，姓侯氏，<placeName key="PL000000003794">太原</placeName>人也。儀容瓌麗，學業精<lb
ed="T" n="0731c14"/>贍，眾典服勤，於《瑜伽論》特振聲彩。<persName key="A002146">天皇大<lb
ed="T" n="0731c15"/>帝</persName>徵為翻經大德。又與<persName key="A001179">勝莊</persName>、<persName key="A002454">大儀</persName>等同參<lb
ed="T" n="0731c16"/><persName key="A001470">義淨</persName>譯場，對<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>敡</sic><corr>敭</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz4"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g666"/>受賜，言謝瀏亮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g667"/>。<ref type="person" target="#A002146">帝</ref>悅，尋授封<lb
ed="T" n="0731c17"/><placeName key="PL000000000531">昌平縣</placeName><persName key="A002451">開國公</persName><ptr target="#n671"/>，累井田至三千戶。<ref type="person" target="#A002146">帝</ref>為讚<lb
ed="T" n="0731c18"/>曰：「<placeName key="PL000000000193">河</placeName><placeName key="PL000000005527">汾</placeName>之寶，<placeName key="PL000000005250">山</placeName><placeName key="PL000000000223">嶽</placeName>之英，早祛俗累，夙解塵<lb
ed="T" n="0731c19"/>纓。緇門仰德，紺宇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g668"/>馳聲。式亞<persName key="A001482">龍樹</persName>，爰齊<persName key="A001003">馬<lb
ed="T" n="0731c20"/>鳴</persName>。」為<ref target="#A002146" type="person">時君</ref>之所貴，為若此也。御製風行，緇<lb
ed="T" n="0731c21"/>伍榮之。後充<placeName key="PL000000023657">河南佛授記寺</placeName>都維那，晚升<lb
ed="T" n="0731c22"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000023657">寺</ref>任，中外肅然。終年六十餘，著《義門》行于<lb
ed="T" n="0731c23"/>世。如其「七方便人迴心漸頓悟」義，與<persName key="A001307">湛法<lb
ed="T" n="0731c24"/>師</persName>為勍敵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g669"/>耳，故交綏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g670"/>而退焉。</p>
